                "key": "Northwind Wolf",
                "string_values": [
                  "<p>DMG dealt by Elemental Skill and Elemental Burst is increased by <span style=\"color: rgb(55, 255, 255)\">16%/20%/24%/28%/32%</span>. When an Elemental Skill hits an opponent, its CRIT Rate will be increased by <span style=\"color: rgb(55, 255, 255)\">2%/2.%5/3%/3.5%/4%</span>. When an Elemental Burst hits an opponent, its CRIT Rate will be increased by <span style=\"color: rgb(55, 255, 255)\">2%/2.5%/3%/3.5%/4%</span>. Both of these effects last 10s separately, have 4 max stacks, and can be triggered once every 0.1s.</p>"
